 for Lebesgue almost every\n$\\beta\\in(1.497\\ldots,2)$ the set $W_{\\beta}(\\omega_{n}\\cdot 2^{-n})$ is of\nfull Lebesgue measure within $[0,\\frac{1}{\\beta-1}]$. Here the sequence\n$(\\omega_{n})_{n=1}^{\\infty}$ should be interpreted as a sequence tending to\ninfinity at a very slow rate.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 25 Jun 2015 15:18:45 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-06-26"}
